Stop being a baby and sit still.

10
00:00:53,261 --> 00:00:54,095
Hear me?

11
00:00:54,179 --> 00:00:56,431
You bastard, what did you say?

12
00:00:56,514 --> 00:00:57,932
Do you have a death wish?

13
00:00:59,434 --> 00:01:02,145
You're making a huge fucking mistake,
you damn thug!

14
00:01:02,729 --> 00:01:03,730
Tell him to shut up.

15
00:01:05,398 --> 00:01:06,274
Gang-yong.

16
