20
00:01:21,873 --> 00:01:22,832
Are you calm now?

21
00:01:22,916 --> 00:01:24,459
GANG-YONG

22
00:01:25,627 --> 00:01:26,669
Answer me.

23
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:29,005
What do you want?

24
00:01:29,589 --> 00:01:32,967
There's a report that came in
from Yeongmoonpo Police Department today.

25
00:01:33,051 --> 00:01:34,385
A guy on a motorcycle slashed

26
