a man's neck with a knife
in a parking lot, then got away.

27
00:01:38,014 --> 00:01:39,057
Write this down.

28
00:01:39,808 --> 00:01:44,479
Seoul, Gangdong, A 6438.

29
00:01:45,146 --> 00:01:48,024
It's a fake plate number,
so it won't show up in the database.

30
00:01:48,525 --> 00:01:50,527
Find where the guy
on this motorcycle went.

31
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,613
In order to find this--

32
00:01:53,696 --> 00:01:55,365
I know it's hard and time-consuming.

33
00:01:56,032 --> 00:01:57,242
That's why I called you.

34
00:01:58,201 --> 00:02:00,453
It's 10:00 p.m. I'll give you five hours.

35
00:02:00,537 --> 00:02:01,913
If you can't find him,

36
00:02:03,456 --> 00:02:06,251
your little cousin's strip show
will go online.

37
00:02:06,334 --> 00:02:09,045
Try to pull something on me,
and it'll also go online.

38
00:02:09,712 --> 00:02:13,258
If you don't want to see lil Group's
stock prices go down tomorrow morning…

39
00:02:13,341 --> 00:02:14,175
Get it done.

40
00:02:18,596 --> 00:02:19,430
What is it?

41
00:02:20,181 --> 00:02:21,599
735629.

42
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,316
See you again.

43
00:02:34,988 --> 00:02:36,156
Fuck!

44
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:10,190
BLOODHOUNDS

45
00:03:17,155 --> 00:03:18,114
Hello, sir.

46
00:03:18,198 --> 00:03:20,074
-Come here, you punk.
-Salute!

47
00:03:20,158 --> 00:03:21,117
Damn it.

48
00:03:21,743 --> 00:03:23,036
Soju's on me. I'll buy.

49
00:03:30,585 --> 00:03:32,212
-This way, sir.
-Thank you.

50
00:03:32,712 --> 00:03:33,922
-Hello, sir.
-Hi.

51
00:03:35,506 --> 00:03:40,011
