when the casino opens?

64
00:04:11,709 --> 00:04:12,710
What do you mean?

65
00:04:13,836 --> 00:04:15,588
Kim Myeong-gil will rake in the money.

66
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:17,006
-I see.
-Gun-woo.

67
00:04:17,507 --> 00:04:18,341
Yes, sir.

68
