205
00:14:19,108 --> 00:14:20,985
In two months. It's a girl.

206
00:14:23,571 --> 00:14:25,698
We've been together for over three years.

207
00:14:26,824 --> 00:14:30,077
If you had family,
you should've told me, you punk!

208
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,746
Come on. Then you would've
told me not to come.

209
00:14:36,792 --> 00:14:38,544
Go home. I'll wrap things up here.

210
00:14:38,627 --> 00:14:40,963
No, it's been a while
since we had a drink together.

211
00:14:41,046 --> 00:14:42,131
I'm staying.

212
00:14:42,214 --> 00:14:43,632
I said go home.

213
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,093
Man, that temper of yours.

214
00:14:49,054 --> 00:14:49,889
Hey.

215
00:14:50,931 --> 00:14:52,266
I'm good. I don't need it.

216
00:14:52,766 --> 00:14:55,352
It's not for you. Get your wife some meat.

217
00:14:55,436 --> 00:14:57,980
Iron intake is important
for pregnant women. Come on.

218
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:01,817
This is too much.

219
00:15:05,195 --> 00:15:06,113
Are you coming?

220
00:15:06,196 --> 00:15:07,323
Yes, I'm coming.

221
00:15:07,406 --> 00:15:09,325
-All right. I'll go on ahead.
-Sure.

222
00:15:11,994 --> 00:15:13,078
Call a cab.

223
00:15:13,162 --> 00:15:15,414
I'll have another smoke
until it gets here.

224
00:15:17,374 --> 00:15:18,208
Yang-jung.

225
00:15:21,795 --> 00:15:22,630
Thanks.

226
00:15:24,048 --> 00:15:25,466
Cut it out.

227
00:15:28,719 --> 00:15:30,512
You're the best.

228
00:15:31,138 --> 00:15:33,307
I'm going to get some hanwoo
on my way back.

229
00:15:38,729 --> 00:15:40,731
Hyeon-ju says she's going to bed first.

230
00:15:40,814 --> 00:15:41,649
Okay.

231
00:15:44,193 --> 00:15:45,027
Are you all right?

232
00:15:45,736 --> 00:15:46,570
Yes, sir.

233
00:15:53,827 --> 00:15:55,496
You must be really worried.

234
00:15:56,163 --> 00:15:59,291
I'm the one who taught Myeong-gil.
He's my responsibility.

235
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:02,211
But after my body broke down like this,

236
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,213
I didn't have the courage

237
00:16:05,839 --> 00:16:06,674
to fight him.

238
00:16:09,385 --> 00:16:10,803
The only thing I could do was

239
00:16:11,887 --> 00:16:14,848
to take care of Hyeon-ju.

240
00:17:25,669 --> 00:17:26,795
Who are you?

241
00:17:27,713 --> 00:17:28,589
Well,

242
00:17:29,673 --> 00:17:30,674
I'm…

243
00:17:32,217 --> 00:17:33,218
your dad's friend.

244
00:17:38,682 --> 00:17:40,934
Don't cry.

245
00:17:41,435 --> 00:17:42,436
Please don't cry.

246
00:17:46,482 --> 00:17:48,484
Dad!

247
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:56,617
CONDOLENCES

248
00:17:57,576 --> 00:17:58,911
What do you mean?

249
00:18:01,288 --> 00:18:05,125
Fill up this hall with the best
condolence flowers you can find.

250
00:18:05,209 --> 00:18:06,043
Yes, sir.

251
00:18:06,126 --> 00:18:09,546
Have ten of our men guard overnight
until they transport the coffin.

252
00:18:10,255 --> 00:18:12,132
-Should we arm them?
-No.

253
00:18:12,633 --> 00:18:14,843
It's because a kid is all by herself.

254
00:18:14,927 --> 00:18:16,178
Tell them to get her fed.

255
00:18:16,261 --> 00:18:17,221
Yes, sir.

256
00:18:18,639 --> 00:18:21,391
Sir, I think you left your scarf inside.

257
00:18:21,475 --> 00:18:22,768
No, never mind that.

258
00:18:25,395 --> 00:18:27,189
By the way, why'd he kill himself?

